Polymarkets new potential mascot. Will Polymarket officially make Poly its mascot?

Context / Background:
A Polymarket team member with a verified badge recently hinted at a potential mascot named Poly and even created a Twitter poll asking if she should become the official mascot. This sparked significant community engagement and speculation around the mascot’s adoption.

Evidence of Demand:
    •    The community independently launched a $POLY coin on Solana inspired by the mascot idea.
    •    The token reached a $2 million market cap, generated $10 million in trading volume, and now has over 3,500 holders.
    •    This demonstrates strong community interest and a clear demand for a market around Poly’s official adoption. The dedicated X community has over 700 active members.

Why This Market Matters:
The mascot concept has organically become one of the most viral Polymarket-related narratives, bridging the prediction market audience with Solana’s meme coin culture. Listing this market would capture a trending cultural event while driving engagement between both communities. People want to bid. Let them.
